<div data-type="solution" id="fs-idp34547536"><p id="fs-idp6445072">The structure that gives zero formal charges is consistent with the actual structure:<span data-type="newline"><br/></span>
</p><span data-type="media" id="fs-idp26230352" data-alt="A Lewis structure shows a nitrogen atom with one lone pair of electrons single bonded to two hydrogen atoms and an oxygen atom which has two lone pairs of electrons. The oxygen atom is single bonded to a hydrogen atom.">
